data.text: @SenatorCollins Explain your lack of support for the SAVE ACT you filthy dirty corrupt POS

@SenatorCollins That aged about as well as this. You're about 18 years past your shelf life which means you've become somewhat fetid, Senator Bobblehead.

https://t.co/lL9WWonUEc

@SenatorCollins How do you justify not supporting the SAVE act? It is quite possibly the most unifying bill ever proposed, the entirety of the US CITIZENS want it, there's really no legitimate excuse.
@SenatorCollins I supported you financially in your 2020 reelection against Sara Gideon. You will need support in '26. Please do the honorable thing and support and pass the SAVE ACT.
